{"tid":218275,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北極熊伴侶一起生活20年，狠遭動物園拆散「心碎而死」！","createTime":"2017-04-26T11:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T23:56:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1feafc6f55931890dc21e1aa10f9bab76cb2e1c","tid":218275,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:31:08.000Z","msg":"北極熊動物同志伴侶母同性戀<br />\nGlobal 國際 / 2017年4月25日 星期二<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gagatai.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_cover-mobile-p-2x/public/image/2017/4399/sdfa.jpg?itok=-aLK8eLG&amp;timestamp=1493114446\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgagatai.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle_cover-mobile-p-2x%2Fpublic%2Fimage%2F2017%2F4399%2Fsdfa.jpg%3Fitok%3D-aLK8eLG%26timestamp%3D1493114446&h=e9805caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國聖地牙哥海洋世界（San Diego SeaWorld）1隻21歲、深受遊客歡迎的母北極熊欣嘉（Szenja）近日突然過世，而她猝死的背後原因被指向是，園方日前送走與牠相伴20年的另一隻母北極熊雪花（Snowflake），同性伴侶被送走使牠深受打擊，才失去求生意志導致死亡，令人相當難過。<br />\n<br />\n飼育員表示，欣嘉是園內的明星動物，擁有大批粉絲的她，在過世一個禮拜前，就已經被注意到身體狀況不佳，不僅昏昏欲睡，也缺乏食慾、不想進食。現在欣嘉已經被送去解剖，真正死因還有待驗屍報告出爐後才能釐清。海洋世界的副園長葛拉佛（Al Garver）表示，「欣嘉是我們深愛的動物家庭成員，這一天對她來說很艱難，我們很開心能夠參與她的生命，並且感謝這20多年來牠對海洋世界的貢獻。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://youtu.be/gd7DjAMRUQE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgd7DjAMRUQE&h=385ff286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（北極熊欣嘉生前玩玩具的模樣。圖／YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n在2月底時，雪花被送到匹茲堡動物園進行「交配」，在此之前兩頭熊已經朝夕相處了20年。當時有許多人連署，希望園方不要把牠們分開，讓雪花和辛嘉繼續相伴，可是連署仍然沒有成功。<br />\n<br />\n不過，善待動物組織「PETA」（People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals，簡稱PETA）的執行副總雷曼（Tracy Remain）認為，欣嘉的死與雪花被送走有關，欣嘉是死於心碎，「海洋世界把牠的朋友送走，只是為了生出更多悲慘的北極熊寶寶，牠只好做出大家都會有的反應，就是放棄生存。」 雷曼說：「這是海洋世界的警訊，應該要停止強制交配、把動物送來送去，讓高齡的動物安養天年。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gagatai.com/sites/default/files/image/2017/4401/fdsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgagatai.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimage%2F2017%2F4401%2Ffdsf.jpg&h=1406210c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（希望北極熊欣嘉能夠安息。圖／PETA臉書）<br />\n<br />\n「PETA」資深副總丹‧馬修（Dan Mathews）也認同雷曼的話，並強調了動物界的同性戀關係並非獨特的現象。「我們已經觀察到自然界有超過500種的同性戀動物，從北極熊到雞都是。這也讓我們了解同性戀是多麼自然的、人類和動物有許多共同之處，以及動物的權利必須得到尊重。」<br />\n<br />\n欣嘉1995年在德國伍珀塔爾的動物園出生，2年後被帶到聖地牙哥海洋世界。一般而言，野生的北極熊可以活18年，在飼養環境下，更可以活到20至30年。而就在14日，美國也失去全國最高齡的北極熊胡魯（Uulu），終年36歲。"},{"pid":"6d305583f57d9839f929bc2d5880f404ff4f9db1","tid":218275,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gagatai.com/news/global/北極熊同志伴侶一起生活20年，狠遭拆散「心碎而死」！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgagatai.com%2Fnews%2Fglobal%2F%E5%8C%97%E6%A5%B5%E7%86%8A%E5%90%8C%E5%BF%97%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB20%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E7%8B%A0%E9%81%AD%E6%8B%86%E6%95%A3%E3%80%8C%E5%BF%83%E7%A2%8E%E8%80%8C%E6%AD%BB%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%81&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr05UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=f5f675a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://gagatai.com/news/global/北極熊同志伴侶一起生活20年，狠遭拆散「心碎而死」！</a>"},{"pid":"afa8e6070efbe95fa1d956cbd94a1bce6617bce0","tid":218275,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466d6e79bd2afd6f958cf74fe55b28c79063bde0","tid":218275,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:02:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18d5fd2d76282fd82129e8dd8effc3a5eaa7462d","tid":218275,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"死耶撚連動物都唔放過要逼害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d42203df240c4b93babbc75ddba1d30f00a8ee","tid":218275,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"關同性事咩<br />\n對廿年乜都有感情啦<br />\n咁得閒就不如捉個毒撚去交配好過"},{"pid":"9b26eba64831c804b106804c9bc6ed94ff2563e8","tid":218275,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e6a3d114fb03ebdd6e03239c7318b8488a0864","tid":218275,"uid":47263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關同性事咩<br />\n對廿年乜都有感情啦<br />\n咁得閒就不如捉個毒撚去交配好過</blockquote><br />\n毒撚單性繁殖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfc368b5dabc21b05a725002ccf8dc039aa0f8a","tid":218275,"uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:28:03.000Z","msg":"好朋友唔得既<br />\n好感情就係同志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915a1e1c0cb83cc6ace98eeba54c68349b0a6f18","tid":218275,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb45d72abfc00cf95f7af25978ffc3ac1f15a1db","tid":218275,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T23:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>關同性事咩<br />\n對廿年乜都有感情啦<br />\n咁得閒就不如捉個毒撚去交配好過</blockquote><br />\n毒撚單性繁殖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚失去雙手會點"}]}